    "The detailed, contextspecific nature of this dataset makes it ideal for systems that require deep, domain-specific knowledge.",
    "Similarly, CovidDialog, released in 2020 in response to the COVID-19 pandemic, offers targeted information on COVID-19 and other pneumonia-related conditions, making it an invaluable resource for QA applications focused on respiratory diseases.",
    "The release dates of these datasets are indicative of their relevance to current healthcare challenges.",
